  "remarks": "As at Aug. 2015, leads Jamaat Tarkhan, a terrorist group that forms part of the\n                Islamic State in Iraq and the Levant, listed as Al-Qaida in Iraq (QDe.115). Wanted\n                by the authorities of the Russian Federation for terrorist crimes committed in its\n                territory, including through an international arrest warrant. Photo available for\n                inclusion in the INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 15 November 2021. INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link:https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Individuals",
